Here is a list of items that are required for a project using an Arduino Board (UNO):
- USB-A to micro-USB cable
- Car chassis
- L298 motor driver module
- Flame sensor module
- Servo Motor
- L293D Motor Driver Module
- Mini DC Submersible Pump
- 12V Battery
- On-Off-Switch
- DC Female Connector Jack
- Connecting wires
- Soldering iron
- Solder wire
- Hot Melt Glue Gun

All of these items are important for the project to function correctly. Please ensure that you have all of them before starting the project.

**Software Required**
Arduino IDE
